On level 3
==========
* 1 Feat
* BL power Death's Gift: resist cold 5, DR5/- NL
* BL spell Chill Touch
* +1 Fort save
* +1 Ref. safe
* 1 extra 1st-level spell/day
* 1 extra 1st-level spell known
* 2+INT skill pts. - 4pts
* 1d6 HP = 2
* Favoured class:- 1 HP, +3 HP this level.
Choices: Spell, Feat, skills
----------------------------
* Feat:- Spell Focus (Necromancy)
* Spell:- Protection From Evil.
* Skills:- Bluff, Religion, Use Magic Device x2.
